th a blowtorch. Possible, but why?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-10-13T04:51:11Z\u0022 title=\u002210/13/2021 04:51  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 13, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-13T05:42:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022kley_sprey_perekleivaemyy_3m_repositiona\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022100.00\u0022 height=\u0022800\u0022 width=\u0022800\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.deloks.ru/upload/iblock/de4/gjoptsmfjcx7o3gvi0zspqb60b2r547f/kley_sprey_perekleivaemyy_3m_repositionable_75_500_ml_1_full.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}